     ─ ───────────────────────────╖ Release ╓────────────────────────────── ─ 
      ─ ──────────────────────────╜  info!  ╙───────────────────────────── ─ 
          

        Slime-san was minding his own business when suddenlyà A giant      
        worm appeared and gobbled him up! Deep within the worm's belly,    
        Slime-san has to face a decision: Be digested by the incoming      
        wall of stomach acid... Or jump, slide and slime his way through   
        the worm and back out its mouth!                                   
                                                                           
        For more info go to : https://store.steampowered.com/app/473530/   
                                                                           
        NOTES: the release is Standalone and updated to v1.30.0, and       
        includes the Following DLC:                                        
                                                                           
          - 20XX - Hawk Character DLC                                      
          - 20XX - Draco Character DLC                                     
                                                                           
                                                                           
        ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~                                               
                                                                           
                                                                           
        1. Unzip & Unrar.                                                  
        2. Run SiMPLEX.exe for install                                     
        3. Use the Shortcut for start the game                             
        4. Have Fun!!!                                                     
                                                                           
                                                                           
        Ripped: "SOME MOVIES and MUSIC"                                    

                                                                             
